Blog displays a list of blogs entries.
To get here click on the word "Blog" on the upper left hand corner. A blog entry is a short article with a title and body of text. They are sorted chronologically. You can view the blog entries by clicking on the title. 

To create a blog entry click on New blog entry at the bottom of the list or the top of the list on the right.

To edit this entry click Edit this entry on the bottom right of the list.
